description: Frankie Dogs is a great gourmet veggie and vegan hot dog cart roaming the streets of Fort Lauderdale in search of hungry foodies. This cart is always serving the best vegan, vegetarian hot dogs for your curbside meals, and now also offers Applegate All-Natural beef hot dogs for those who want a little meat in their life now and then. Find them near you, and get a delicious bite to eat!
name: Frankie Dogs Gourmet
